Q1. Let us work on the menu of a library. Create a structure containing book information like accession number, name of author, book title
and flag to know whether a book is issued or not. Create a menu in which the following can be done.
1 - Display book information
2 - Add a new book
3 - Display all the books in the library of a particular author
4 - Display the number of books of a particular title
5 - Display the total number of books in the library

